sig
  bpm 130
  system 12tet western
  scale C chromatic

arr
  main 32 |kft

tracks
  1 audio |lmq
    type audio
    strip tivraStrip
  2 midi |nna
    type midi
    plugin tivra4OSC
    strip tivraStrip

returns
  0 Hall |rgl
    fx tivraHall
    strip tivraStrip
  1 Plate |rfc
    fx tivraPlate
    strip tivraStrip
  2 Delay |rhx
    fx tivraDelay
    strip tivraStrip
  3 Color |rag
    fx tivraDistortion
    strip tivraStrip

sec main
